Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.47,0:03:05.01,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}物語は終わり
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.01,0:03:07.35,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}勇者は眠りにつく
