Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.50,0:03:30.66,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}生きている
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.25,0:03:32.88,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}同じ途を選んだ
