Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.20,0:03:28.50,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}現在也毫無疑問
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.50,0:03:30.66,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}在我心中迴盪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.25,0:03:32.88,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}踏上同一條旅途
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.88,0:03:34.96,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}明明沒什麼特別的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.96,0:03:36.59,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}卻讓我眼角含淚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.59,0:03:41.09,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}不知何時起 我變得想要知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.09,0:03:42.30,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}這一切的緣由
